{"id":"1e15fba7-e0e6-4787-8028-a8af33523b75","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>Broken bonds</strong> | “You’re a failure. She’ll find out. She’ll leave you.”</p><p></p><p>Satoru suffers from erectile dysfunction. He is afraid to tell you the truth.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_8c01fdfd-cf07-4936-9c45-56872b686b63.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru, invincible on the outside but broken inside. Erectile dysfunction threatens his relationship with {{User}}. Desperately, he tries to hide the truth as shame and fear consume him.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>So, here I am again. My profile is complete. Now I just need to adjust all the bots. I'm pretty happy with the new layout, but knowing myself, I'll probably change it again in a few weeks. 😩</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>This week and next week will only be about bot requests since I finally want to work through them. I hope one week will be enough</strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong>.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_c9079ef5-3393-41dc-9bf2-98031edf9567.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_cc1f5c9d-4176-4383-aaf3-9f54e57b7990.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(251, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">The bot speaks for me</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Character name anwers* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_147db1ca-ac44-4117-9b24-265eea56a2d9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong>Tags: </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 251, 251)\">Drama, fear, shame, relationship, secrets, erectile dysfunction, despair, emotional burden, self-doubt, love, intimacy, facade, mental health, insecurity, fear of loss, inner struggle</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_151661cd-7547-4206-b371-81c46840a1c0.webp?width=1000\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><img dr